beer.beer_description: A carefully selected combination of malts including Golden Promise, Munich and Caramalt (to name a few) combine to create a complex malt flavour and the characteristic red hue of this flagship beer. US hops Simcoe, Amarillo, Centennial and Chinook are added throughout the process adding an earthy spiciness to the aroma and flavour.
